{"title":"redis安装","uid":"5a4681c603f0c9d9a46ed22467ed2217","slug":"redis安装","date":"2022-05-18T14:11:38.513Z","updated":"2022-05-18T14:40:10.234Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/redis安装.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"centos安装\"><a href=\"#centos安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"centos安装\"></a>centos安装</h2><p><strong>官方snapd商店安装</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> yum <span class=\"token function\">install</span> epel-release -y\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> yum <span class=\"token function\">install</span> snapd -y \n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> systemctl <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">enable</span> --now snapd.socket \n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">ln</span> -s /var/lib/snapd/snap /snap\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> snap <span class=\"token function\">install</span> redis<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>官方源码安装[推荐]</strong></p>\n<p>1.安装阿里源</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># CentOS 7</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">wget</span> -O /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo http://mirrors.aliyun.com/repo/Centos-7.repo<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>2.安装编译器</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yum <span class=\"token function\">install</span> gcc-c++ -y<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>3.下载源码</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">wget</span> https://download.redis.io/redis-stable.tar.gz<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>4.编译redis</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">tar</span> -xzvf redis-stable.tar.gz\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> redis-stable\n<span class=\"token function\">make</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>5.安装生成的可执行文件</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">make</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>6.启动redis</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">redis-server<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n","text":"centos安装官方snapd商店安装 sudo yum install epel-release -y sudo yum install snapd -y sudo systemctl enable --now snapd.socket sudo ln -s /var/lib/...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":506,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"redis","slug":"redis","count":2,"path":"api/tags/redis.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#centos%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">centos安装</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Potter","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"www.baidu.com","description":"个人学习爱好者","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/BJPotter","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"简单动态字符串","uid":"f92ea47dc1903826eb6db17b7056431f","slug":"redis字符串","date":"2022-05-18T14:08:05.719Z","updated":"2022-05-18T15:08:18.426Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/redis字符串.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"简单动态字符串 ​ Redis没有使用C语言的字符串，而是自己构建了一种名为简单动态字符串SDS（simple dynamic string）的抽象类型，并把sds用作默认redis的默认字符串表示。 ​ Redis数据库里面的键值对最底层都是由SDS实现的 SDS定义C语言表示...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":313,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"redis","slug":"redis","count":2,"path":"api/tags/redis.json"}],"author":{"name":"Potter","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"www.baidu.com","description":"个人学习爱好者","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/BJPotter","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}}}